cs.SD, cs.IR, cs.MM, cs.CL, cs.LG 

The paper focuses on introducing a free and open dataset of audio clips for research related to data mining in audio archives of field recordings/soundscapes. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including cs.SD (Sound), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.MM (Multimedia), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.LG (Machine Learning). However, given the emphasis on data mining and auto-tagging, cs.SD and cs.IR are the most likely categories, followed by cs.MM, cs.CL, and cs.LG.
